    public class NexMarkProducer

    This class simply generates auctions, bids, persons and items for an online bidding system analytics system. It is part of Dominik Schroeck's master thesis for DIMA/DFKI

    • Constructor Detail

      • NexMarkProducer

        public NexMarkProducer(java.lang.Long pause,
                       int bids_per_step_low,
                       int bids_per_step_max,
                       java.lang.Long ChangeInterval,
                       int producer_id)
        Constructor. Initializes categories and pulls CSV files for cities and item names.
        Parameters:
        pause - Pause between two subsequent Production Intervals
        bids_per_step_low - Minimum number of bids per interval, all other events are produced at a fraction of this, consult the thesis for more details
        bids_per_step_max - Maximum number of bids per interval
        ChangeInterval - Interval in which to (randomly) change the bids per step during execution
        producer_id - ID of this producer thread
